  "title": "6 months contract Food QC Analyst #HJN",
  "description": "<p>Duties: </p><ul><li>Perform inspections on raw materials, intermediates and finished products by conduct sensory evaluation, carry out physical, analytical tests to ensure compliance with specifications and standards.</li><li>Perform basic checks, calibration and maintenance of test equipment to ensure that test results are accurate.</li><li>Assist and support in non-conformance and investigations of customers’ complaint samples or rejected items (Internal & External).</li><li>Manage the overall QC status of all final products and perform SAP for final products to facilitate shipment.</li><li>Ensure lab stock is sufficient for lab use.</li></ul><p>Working hours: Mon-Fri office hours<br /><br />Requirements: </p><ul><li>Min Dip/Deg in Food Science/ Technology/ relevant equivalent educational qualifications</li><li>No Food Allergy/ Restrictions</li></ul><p>Janeve: <a href=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/wa.me/6588183965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wa.me/6588183965</a></p><p>OR</p><p>Email me at janeve.ng@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>EA Personnel : Janeve Ng Choy Tong </p><p>C.E.I: R25159176</p><p>Company Registration No: 99C4599</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd\n\n<a href=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/wa.me/6588183965\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
